text: Anne Dickmann (born 12 February 1958) is a German rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Düsseldorf
